text.tspan: 2022 University of California Contract Ratification Vote

tspan.tspan: In December of 2022, Academic Student Employees and Student Researchers
voted to Ratify the Tentative Agreements. With a historically high turnout of
18,483 ASEs and 14,697 SRs, both groups voted to ratify the tentative agreement.
In the below map, one dot equals 100 votes
